                  </persName>
            . I left my tools at New-court while I went<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181907070013"></xptr>to breakfast. When I returned they were gone. The court is no thouroughfare.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to. )</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. A man whom I know asked me to carry them to the Red Lion in Fore-street.</p>
